  ('dietitian-moex-04444', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於降血糖藥物的主要作用機制，下列敘述何者正確？', '["sulfonylureas類抑制腸道對葡萄糖的吸收", "biguanides類刺激胰臟β-cell分泌胰島素", "thiazolidinediones類減少周邊組織對葡萄糖的利用率", "acarbose為α-glucosidase抑制劑，延緩醣類吸收"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4a5f2c07c6ff", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ca5cb7bf2305", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
